text: William Killen is the name of: * William Killen (chief justice) (1722–1805), Irish born first chief justice and first chancellor under the Constitution of 1792 of the state of Delaware, USA * William Dool Killen (1806–1902), Irish Presbyterian minister and church historian * William M. Killen (born 1938), American politician * William Wilson Killen (1860–1939), Australian politician
title: William Killen
